<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>外防输入</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>勇挑重担</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200820/e02db6a53ec243eaaa56456f1abfb4b5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200820/7949e1e9f3b043248b090017f9ac5a3a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
